<plot>Twilight follows a diverse group of characters coping with their own sorrows, confusions, and answered questions. Their lives intersect on a busy small city street. Their attention is captured by a sage-like poet, his words shedding light on their collective sadness. Twilight confronts the issues of love, violence, and self-destruction while exploring the function of time, the scope of our universe, and the transcendent nature of humanity.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?621946</url></doc>
